Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the\nshards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku's a bit lecherous,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he carries the burden of\NNaraku's curse, the Wind Tunnel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he sense the same sadness in her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:21.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poor thing. You got lost\nin the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Koyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did something happen\nto your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no kin anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have nowhere to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:12.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was a beautiful woman\nwith skin as white as snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, because I once trained here,\NI know these parts well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what about that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I was still a\nrosy-cheeked child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snow at this time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How wonderful!\NWhat a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Excuse me.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lately, a snow demon has\nbeen appearing hereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Several village men\nhave been found like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better to return to the hut\nand tell everyone about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll put an end to the demon,\nso it won't make any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense too much evil.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That monk was quite a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon is supposed to be\na vision with skin as white as snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most men would be mesmerized\nand follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sign of Naraku here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was cleaning out\nmy backpack and found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I brought it to play\nwith everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure\nit didn't get damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sparkler. A sparkler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snow... now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be having\ntrouble in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:28.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:34.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss... will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please hold him.\NYour child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, let's eat this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No work, no food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't need to share\nwith the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a greedy guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Followed the smell of\nthe fish, didja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NIt was the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder it's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where're Sango and Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They'll get hungry and come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That fish belongs to\NKirara and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mere Kagome and eat.\NIt's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry for making ourselves home\nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NIt's snowing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boar meat.\NIt'll warm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's still raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so uncouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:17.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better to stay here until\nthe Snow Maiden passes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snow Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. If a young man walks alone\non a day like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a young woman stops him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if he follows her,\nit's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The next day, he's found\npitifully frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this woman is as fair\nas the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I end up frozen,\NI'd like to see her just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But isn't Sango with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, then it's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't understand at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:57.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if Miroku would leave\nsuch a woman alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The question is:\NHow will Sango react.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gives me the shivers just\nthinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango has feelings... for Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many times have we\ndiscussed this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he never gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If this one's another demon who's causing\ntrouble due to Naraku's disappearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we can't ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:27.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a special restorative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sango!\N- Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drink this! It's a restorative!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's supposed to work wonders when\nyou're chilled to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! It does work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a mixture of potent wine,\nviper, newt and worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:23.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you forgotten?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've already borne him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please hold your child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's living happily...\nthe family of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A barrier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:01.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now please come, my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman is not of this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why does she harm humans?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does she kill men and\nsuck out their life spirit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dear, please keep them company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will prepare rice gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The diapers are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But all these children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have not forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard it with my own ears!\NAbout his child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Maybe it's time for\nhim to settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This may be the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take a demon's words\nso seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is coming...\nfrom inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tear it apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't blow your nose\non my kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My staff is not a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yosaku needs to be fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sutematsu's diaper needs to be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And please sing Otora a lullaby\nand put her to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.\NDon't cry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's change your diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock-a-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't pee over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:23.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The toilet is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been taking care of all\nthese children alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every mother does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But are they all mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Children whose villages were burned\ndown in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Children who were parted from\ntheir mothers right after birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As I took care of such children,\nthey grew in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All of them are so pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful... it's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that Miroku singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess even he will dote\non his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:25.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:27.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:37.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's sleeping soundly.\NGood girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a good girl.\NGrow up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a good baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:55.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hushaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Appear! Snow panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so cold, Kirara can't transform\nto full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Defeat them and take possession\nof the Sacred Jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Done!\NSuch an easy prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Umm...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was there some disturbance outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some stray dogs got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:44.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not worry.\NWe'll chase them out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blast you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The children!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have my senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then look good and hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You resemble a woman I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I didn't want to be\nrough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't taste good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- She's so fast!\N- Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She withstood it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hatred... Full of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:18:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would one so kind-hearted\ndeceive men and do harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate... I hate this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate being born into\na world like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find eternal peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heat! Their weakness is heat and fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! My fox fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not working at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that a snow demon, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! All at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That spirit isn't possessed by\nthe Snow Maiden any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:25.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is the soul of a woman who\ndied because of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She gathered the spirits of the\nchildren who left this world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and took care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A snow demon took possession of\nthat spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's too much suffering in the world\nof wars... especially for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you follow her when\nshe told you she had your kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must've remembered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He IS a fool, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku purposely fell under her spell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to save the\npoor demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... that's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:14.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku would never\nmake such a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really resembled her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who saved me that day\nwhen I was still a youth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Koyuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she's living happily\nsomewhere in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Parting snow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The northern mountains just ahead\nof where Naraku disappeared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wolf-Demon tribe who live there\nhave been attacked by a specter,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:53.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the name of Kyokotsu who\npossesses a Sacred Jewel shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why you...! You rose up\nfrom the grave?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna take\nyour Sacred Jewel shard, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neither human nor demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the goal of this\nresurrected specter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next on Inuyasha:\N"Assault on the Wolf-Demon Tribe!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget it! We avenge my comrades first!{\i0}
